column5: heys guys ,thinking of going to these lakes in a few weeks .any info you can give me as far as what to expect.want to camp on crownland.will be taking a 14ft boat and truck with truck camper.any info would be great! thanks
I fished arethusa 1 day third week in june. killed the walleyes on rattletraps,jigs,spinners.great lake,next year we are going to fish it three days.
